'''Georgetown Little Theatre''' is a [[community theatre]] group based in [[Georgetown, Ontario|Georgetown]], [[Ontario]]. Formed in 1960, it is one of the oldest continuously existing community theaters in [[Canada]]. The theater group performs regularly at the John Elliott Theatre.

